description: The video shows a close-up of a window with blinds. The blinds are closed, and the camera is pointed up at the top of the window frame. The blinds are white, and the window frame is grey. The blinds are slightly shaking, and the window pane is wet. The date and time, 2024-08-07 08:41:05, are displayed in the top left corner. The sound of a bird chirping is heard in the background.

The video shows a woman in a pink shirt and green shorts walking across a kitchen, then taking a blue shirt from a chair, and finally sitting down. There are various things on the kitchen counter, including a bowl of eggs, a coconut, bananas, and pots and pans. There is a stove on the right with a black and red lid, and a blue and yellow backpack is to the right of it. There is a light fixture hanging from the ceiling. The date and time of the recording are displayed in the top left corner.

The video is a black and white security camera recording from a closed store. The camera is positioned in a corner of the store, facing a small white refrigerator.  A black chair is visible in the foreground. The store's metal roll-up door is visible to the left, closed and shut.  An object with a fan is visible to the right.  There is a tv screen that has a date and time visible. The date is 2024-08-07 and the time is 04:04:24.  The video shows the store is completely empty and dark. There is no sound.  A very faint beep can be heard at the end of the recording.

The video is a security camera recording of a small dog with black and white fur on the porch of a house. The porch has steps made of tiles and a wooden cabinet with a blue bucket sitting on top of it. The dog walks around the porch, sniffs a white bucket with water in it, and then lies down and takes a nap on the top step. The ground around the porch is mostly dirt with a few rocks scattered on it. The date and time of the recording are displayed in the upper left-hand corner of the screen: 08/07/2024 07:00:45.  It is unclear if there are other items on the porch but these are not in view of the camera. The video ends as the dog continues to sleep.

The video shows a static shot of a blue sky with white clouds. In the background there is a mountain range with trees on the right side.  At the bottom of the frame, there are a few houses and buildings.  The video has a timestamp in the top left corner that reads "2024-08-07 16:05:30." In the background there are sounds of birds chirping and what sounds like a car driving in the distance.  At the end of the video, a low-pitched "p" sound can be heard.

The video shows a security camera view of a kitchen. The camera is positioned near a double-door entryway. The camera captures the movement of a person entering the kitchen with a broom. The kitchen is messy with a small potted plant, a red crate, and a number of miscellaneous items. A large cabinet is visible to the left of the camera. The camera shows a view of the kitchen's right side, which includes white cabinets, a black oven, and a large metal pot sitting on the counter. The person enters the kitchen, sweeps the floor, and exits through the double doors.

The video shows a black and white nighttime view of a backyard patio from inside a house. A window separates the camera from the view. The patio has a pool with several loungers and a table with chairs in the foreground. The Arizona flag flies proudly from a flagpole on the back wall. The video is shot in a fisheye lens with a wide-angle view. The time stamp reads August 7, 2024, at 5:28:21 am. There are a few string lights hanging overhead.

The video is in black and white and shows the interior of a living room. There is a couch, a coffee table with items on it, and some kitchen cabinets in the background. A person walks from the kitchen to the living room wearing a loose-fitting dress, and disappears from view in the living room after a few seconds. A soft, rhythmic thumping sound is heard that gets progressively louder toward the end of the clip.

The video is a black and white night-time recording from a security camera. It shows the view from outside of a house with a screen door. The door opens and a person wearing dark clothing walks inside. The person is seen to be carrying a white object. The date and time of the recording is displayed in the top left corner.  The "Kami" logo is in the bottom left corner.

The video shows a nighttime black and white security camera view of a backyard.  A car is parked on the left side of the frame.  There is a tree with branches in the background of the video.  On the right side is a structure with a wooden frame and metal panels.  Some items are visible on a table in the background.  The video is very dark, but you can hear a bird or other animal making a noise at 0:27.

The video shows a black and white night vision recording of a living room. There are two cats in the room, one lying down near the center of the room and another standing near the left side of the screen. There is a TV on a stand, a small table, and some other furniture in the background. The cats are not moving for most of the clip, except for the standing cat who turns its head at the end of the clip. The camera seems to be mounted on a wall. The recording also shows a date and time stamp in the top left corner of the screen.

The video shows a street corner in a residential area. There is a silver car parked at the edge of the frame. It is partially obscured by a black tarp. A sign that says 'PARE' which is Spanish for 'Stop', is visible in the street, in front of the car. A motorcycle drives by in the street, followed by a small red car. The scene is overcast, but the street is dry.

The video shows a living room with a large brown leather sectional sofa and a coffee table in front of it. There are a couple of pillows on the sofa, and a small, red blanket. A ceiling fan is spinning slowly, and an arched window with white curtains behind it. A large, framed picture is leaning against the wall. A white, metal speaker is on the coffee table, next to a box of tissues. The camera is pointed at a doorway leading into another room, where a person can be heard talking. The person is talking about a friend who's trying to do something.  The person says, “I'm trying to get him to do this thing. But, okay." The video ends with the sound of the person's voice.
The video shows a close-up of a white wall, a brown piece of wood, and some green leaves. The video is shaky and the audio is just wind. It's a short video with no real content.

The video is black and white and was likely taken from a security camera. It is a wide shot of a man sleeping in bed. The man is wearing a white shirt and has a tattoo on his left shoulder. The camera is positioned on a nightstand near the bed and is facing the man's head. The man’s left hand is raised in the air and he appears to be reaching for a stainless steel water bottle on the nightstand. The nightstand also has a lit candle next to the water bottle. The video plays audio of the man snoring loudly.

The video is a security camera footage of a suburban street corner. There are three houses visible in the video. The camera is mounted on the front porch of one of the houses. There is a white round table in the foreground with a blue funnel, a white object, and a white object on top of it. The footage is taken in the morning, and the sun is shining brightly. There are several cars driving by on the street in the background. At the 00:30 mark, a bird can be heard chirping.

The video shows a living room with a TV playing in the background. There is a person sitting on the couch and a woman sitting at a table with a walker next to her. The woman is holding a piece of paper and a pen and appears to be writing. There is a black cat on the couch with the person.

The video is a security camera recording from inside a living room. There is a large white sectional couch and an end table with a few things on it in the background. In the foreground, there is a large dog crate with a blanket in the bottom. In the video, a dog can be heard barking in the background of the video, and then a human voice says, "Hey, please stop! Stop it! Stop!"

The video is a black and white security camera recording. The camera is mounted high on the wall, looking down onto a living room. The room is in the middle of the day, and the light is coming from a window to the left of the camera. A large couch is positioned in the center of the room, with the back facing the camera. A large blanket is draped over the back of the couch. There are many stuffed animals on the couch. To the right of the couch is a large open doorway. In the doorway, you can see a glimpse of a kitchen with a dining table and chairs. There are other objects in the living room, but they are not in focus and are difficult to make out. Someone appears to be moving in the stairway just out of view of the camera.

The video is in black and white and shows a black car parked in front of a house. The car is parked in the middle of a driveway with a wooden fence to the left of the car and a door to the right. There is a motorbike behind the car, partially hidden by some plants. The video was taken on 2024-08-07 at 05:00:04.

The video is a black and white surveillance footage from a security camera. The camera is pointing at a white SUV parked on a street. The SUV is parked facing away from the camera. In the background, a second car is parked on the other side of the street. The time stamp in the top left corner of the video indicates the date and time is 08/07/2024 06:17:41. The camera’s night vision is working well, and it is clear enough to see the vehicles and the street. The video shows the SUV stationary throughout the entire clip, which is 59 seconds in duration. The only changes seen are the time stamp updating and a flicker of light emanating from a street lamp in the distance in the background.

The video is a security camera footage taken from a window looking out on a backyard. The backyard is grassy and has patio furniture, an umbrella, and a fire pit.  In the background there is a body of water with some houses across the water.  The date and time stamp on the video is 08/07/2024 17:00:37. It is a sunny day and there is wind blowing, causing the umbrella to sway and the water to ripple.  The person in the video appears to be a man and he is standing in the background at a table.

The video is a 28-second clip of a baby's room, taken from a security camera. The camera is positioned in the top corner of the room looking down. The room has brown wood floors, and the walls are white. The room has a set of four brown wooden closet doors in the left side of the room, and the right side of the room has a baby bed with a camo-print mattress cover and a grey wooden frame.  The bed has a large blue beanbag chair in front of it.  A small wooden table and chairs are in the bottom left corner of the room, and a blue baby chair is next to the bean bag chair.  The room is full of toys, including a yellow school bus, and a stuffed animal, and there is a small potted plant on the floor to the right of the blue baby chair.  The room is bright and sunny, with light shining through the window curtains that are visible in the background. The camera records 28 seconds of this room with no movement.

The video is a black and white recording from a security camera. It shows a woman wearing a blue shirt and light pants walking through a living room. The woman is carrying a purse in her right hand. The woman walks towards a door on the left side of the video, and looks at something off-screen. She then turns around and continues walking towards the door. As the woman nears the door, she appears to be crying. The camera's timestamp reads 08/07/2024 17:30:10, suggesting the incident occurred on August 7, 2024 at 5:30 PM. There is no audio in the video. The caption reads, “She opened the white picket gates appearing to step onto his property and slowly took off her sunglasses revealing her black eyes. I'm Frances the brown. She said quietly. And the driver who almost hit you just...she found tears burning her eyes and waited patiently knowing about her and knowing her tears were ashamed, kissing.” The caption suggests the woman is experiencing a traumatic event. It is unclear if the woman is the victim of the incident or if she is the driver who almost hit someone.

The video shows a backyard with a screened-in pool. There are two palm trees and some bushes. Beyond the pool, there is a lake with a fountain. In the distance, there are houses. The sky is blue and there are a few clouds.

The video is in black and white and shows a close up of a cluttered corner of a room. There is a white printer sitting on a cabinet that has a stack of boxes and a black bag sitting on the top. There are items hanging off of the cabinet behind the boxes and there is a white cabinet to the right of the printer with a single sheet of paper on it.  To the right of the cabinet is a gray, plastic, file container with a black handle. The video is silent and the camera is static.  At the end of the video, there is a series of soft beeping sounds.

The video shows the inside of a barbershop, with several people waiting for their turn to get a haircut. The barber is cutting a young boy’s hair. A man is talking in Spanish, but it’s difficult to understand what he is saying. Other customers are on their phones or chatting with each other. The barber shop is nicely decorated. There is a large mirror on the back wall, and the floors are tiled. The video is shot from a security camera mounted on the ceiling.

The video is a black and white, night-vision recording from a security camera in a bedroom.  The bed is positioned directly in front of the camera and is made up with dark bedding. A person is lying in the bed, sleeping beneath the covers, their head and shoulders hidden. The bed is a large, wooden bed with a carved headboard. The headboard has a patterned design, possibly of scrolls.  There is a nightstand on the right side of the bed, with a table lamp on it. The lamp is lit. There are some objects on the nightstand, but it's too dark to discern what they are.  On the left side of the bed is a dresser that is also covered in objects. A framed picture hangs above the dresser, on the wall.  There is a door on the far right of the video, with a white doorframe.  The room is dark, with the light from the table lamp providing the only illumination.  There are no other visible signs of life in the room.  The ceiling fan is visible in the top right of the frame, and it is not rotating.

This is a black and white video from a security camera. It's a living room with a couch, a small table with a glass of water, some snacks, a tissue box, and a chair. A person is in the room. We see his back as he walks into the room. He then walks past the camera to the couch. He sits down and uses a tablet.  The date and time of the video is 08/07/2024 08:45:30.

The video shows a security camera view of a street and a closed garage door.  There are sounds of cars driving by in the background and the occasional bird chirping.  A woman walks past the camera and approaches the closed garage door at 1:00.  The woman is wearing a grey tank top, black pants, and a blue backpack.  She is carrying a black bag in her left hand. She stops in front of the door and appears to be looking for something.  The camera's audio picks up a conversation between two people who are speaking Spanish but it is not clear what they are discussing. The video ends with the woman walking away from the door.

The video shows a black pickup truck driving down a street. The truck is driving past a parked orange car. The video is grainy and the quality is poor. There is a date and time stamp in the top left corner of the video: 2021-08-07 08:21:45. The camera appears to be pointed at the street from the perspective of the orange car's front passenger-side. The video is very short, lasting only 15 seconds.

The video shows a man in a grey shirt standing in front of a glass display case that holds what appears to be desserts. He is facing the camera, looking at a piece of paper that is in his hand. He is in a brightly lit store with purple walls and a wooden counter in front of him. On the counter there is a laptop, an iPad, and a microwave. Behind the man, there is a sign that says “Miles Of Sweetness”. A red wreath, some flowers, and a trash can are visible in the video as well. The man is holding a piece of paper that is partly visible to the viewer. The video lasts for less than 30 seconds.  The man does not move in the video, he only shifts his weight slightly.  As the man is looking at the paper, he seems to be comparing the paper with what is inside the glass case. It is difficult to hear any sound in the video.

This is a video from a doorbell camera. The video starts with a white car parked in the driveway in front of a garage door. A woman in a light blue shirt and dark pants walks from the left of the screen toward the car, seemingly checking the car to make sure it is locked. She then continues walking toward a trash can behind the car, looking inside. A dog is walking around the car, sniffing it. Behind the garage door, a truck is partially visible. To the right of the driveway is a brick house with windows visible. The camera is pointed at a slight upward angle. The woman bends down to the trash can. Then she stands up and moves slightly to the right, possibly looking for something. This is when a trash can lid falls to the ground. The woman continues looking around and moves her hands, seemingly looking for something. The dog is sniffing around the yard. The woman walks behind the car and the video ends.

The video shows a dog entering a crate. The dog is a medium sized, brown and tan, short-haired dog. It is in a living room with a wood floor and white walls. The camera is positioned in a corner of the room. The video begins with the dog jumping down from a couch. It then walks over to its crate and sniffs around the inside. The dog then enters the crate and lays down. It appears to be chewing on a toy that is inside the crate.  The video ends with the dog still laying in its crate.

The video shows a night time view of a parking lot as seen from inside a building. The lot is wet from rain, and the cars are parked in rows. There is a white van on a hill overlooking the lot. There is a single light post illuminating the lot.

The video is from a security camera inside a home. The camera is pointing towards a doorway leading to the outside. The time is 08/20/2021 1:29:22. A small dog is lying on the ground outside the door. There are trees and bushes visible through the open door. To the right of the door there is a large, wooden chair with red and brown upholstery. The chair is positioned in front of a fireplace.

The video shows a young woman with her hair up in a bun, walking from left to right in a kitchen. She is wearing a black t-shirt with a white print and black pants.  The kitchen is clean and modern, with white cabinets and a black stove and exhaust hood. There is a sink and a white countertop to the right of the stove. The walls are white, and there is a giraffe figurine on the wall behind the sink. In the background, you can see a shelf with dishes and other kitchen supplies. There is a door on the right side of the frame, and a red metal chair to the right of the door. The floor is a light wood laminate.  The sound is of the woman walking and the kitchen sounds like the fridge being open, the faucet turning on, and the water running.

The video shows a security camera recording from inside a house. The camera is positioned to the left of a bed with a floral pattern bedspread. The person in the video is standing at the bedroom door, which is open, and walking towards the camera. The person is holding a black leather duffle bag and a cell phone in their right hand. The camera catches the person’s reflection in a full-length mirror located on the right side of the room. The person is wearing a gray shirt, jeans, and a black watch. The person says, "We need to get an air conditioner, huh? I’m going to try. Oh, Really? All right." It seems the person is talking to someone else in the house but the camera is only recording the person near the door. The date and time are stamped on the top left corner of the video: 08/07/2024 16:29:37.  The video ends at 08/07/2024 16:30:11.  The person's actions and the sound of their voice suggest that the person is going to try to use the air conditioner.  The room is well-lit and appears to be clean and tidy.

The video is shot from a doorbell camera looking through a screen door and a bush. A man is mowing the lawn in front of a house. He is wearing a peach colored shirt and a hat. He is mowing the lawn using a riding lawnmower. There is a trash can in the yard and two other cars parked on the street. The date 08/07/2024 09:16:58 is displayed in the top left corner of the video.  The lawnmower makes a “P” sound.

The video shows a person in shorts and a grey t-shirt opening a door to a room. Inside the room, a black metal dog crate is visible. The person is looking around the room, and we can hear them saying "pee-pee". They are likely looking for their dog and wondering where it went. It appears as if their dog may have had an accident in the crate, as the person appears to be concerned.

The video is a night-time security camera recording of a person sitting on a couch, tying their shoe. The camera angle is from behind them, and you can only see their lower half and the furniture in the room. The person is sitting on a couch with a white pillow, and their feet are resting on the floor. They are wearing dark shorts and dark sneakers. Behind them, to the left, there is a white stool and a table with some items on it. The video is in black and white and is grainy, which suggests that it is from a night vision camera. The timestamp in the top left corner of the video says 08/07/2024 05:34:07. The video is only 30 seconds long and shows the person tying their shoe. There are no other details or context available from the video.

The video is from a security camera and shows the inside of a living room. A couch is in the background with a small toy in the foreground. There is a door in the background as well. There is a small table with four chairs off to the left of the camera.  The sound in the video is of a child crying.

The video is from a security camera in a garage. The camera is mounted high on the wall, pointing downwards. The garage is dimly lit with the only light source coming from a single light bulb. The video is in black and white. The camera pans slowly across the garage, showing a variety of objects including a bicycle, a table covered with a blanket, chairs, a small wagon, a toolbox and other various boxes. The camera is positioned so that it can see through a large window that is at the back of the garage. There is an animal noise at the end of the video. It is possible that the animal is a cat as cats are often seen in garages.

The video starts with a view of a red car parked in the driveway of a house.  The camera is positioned at the bottom of a set of stairs leading up to the front door. A woman is walking toward the car, holding a brown purse. She stops to rummage through the purse before opening the car door and getting in. She then starts the car and drives away. The camera remains fixed on the driveway. The video is shot in a suburban neighborhood. It is a sunny day, and there is a clear view of a house in the background. The house is a one-story brick house with a garage. It is likely that the video was recorded by a home security camera. The woman in the video might be the homeowner. The video captures her daily routine of driving away from her home.

The video is a still shot of a hallway in an apartment. A closed wooden door is in the foreground. The camera is pointed directly at the door. The wall on the left is white and has a coat rack on it with a green jacket hanging on it. On the table below, we can see a glass jar, and a red object with a book on top. The wall to the right of the door is a light blue. On the wall is a white light switch.  Next to that is a ladder bookshelf with a few items on it. At the top of the door, there is a bird sitting on a metal bar, and it makes a series of chirping sounds.  A Yi security camera logo is in the lower left-hand corner of the video.

The video is from a security camera inside a home. It shows the date and time as 08/07/2024 07:05:55 in the top left corner. A person wearing a baseball cap can be seen walking through the doorway at the back of the room. They are facing away from the camera. The person is holding a cell phone to their ear and is talking. The camera is partially blocked by a gray curtain with a white mandala design. There is a dark brown chair in front of the curtain. The wall to the left of the doorway is a peach color. There is a white door to the right of the doorway. The camera is a Kami brand camera, as indicated by the logo in the lower left corner. The video is silent.

The video shows a backyard with a white picket fence in the background. There is a red ball on the grass near the fence. At the bottom of the screen, there is a large piece of black tarp which is surrounded by some metal pieces and other materials. The camera is stationary and the time stamp in the top left corner of the screen shows that the recording took place on August 7, 2024, at 10:22 PM. The video continues with a variety of bird calls audible in the background.  The video shows a very still scene with no motion for the duration of the recording.

The video shows a bush with green leaves in the foreground, a small patch of green grass, and a street with several parked cars in the background. The camera is positioned on the edge of the roof overlooking the bush. The date and time are shown in the top left corner: 08/07/2024 14:02:09. A small "kami" logo is shown in the bottom left corner. There is no movement in the video, except for the leaves in the bush that rustle slightly from the wind. A bird can be heard chirping faintly in the background. The video ends with a bird's call: "Peep."

The video is black and white and appears to be taken from a security camera. It is in night vision mode. The timestamp in the upper left corner shows that the video was taken on August 7, 2024 at 13:17. The video starts with a person in a loose-fitting dress or robe walking towards a refrigerator. They open the refrigerator and look inside. The person then reaches into the refrigerator, grabs a bottle, and walks away from the camera. The camera then pans out to show the entire kitchen. There is a stove, a refrigerator, a small table with two chairs, a couch, and two framed pictures on the wall. The person is no longer visible in the video. The video ends with the camera focused on the kitchen counter, which is covered in a marble-like surface. A "kami" watermark is visible in the bottom left corner of the screen.

The video shows a man in a garage, getting into a black and red utility vehicle with a roll cage, and then driving it out of the garage.  The garage is cluttered with various items, including a large fan, buckets, gas cans, a ladder, a sprayer, and a second utility vehicle. The camera is positioned so that the yellow strap of the vehicle is in the foreground, obstructing a clear view of the garage and man. The garage has a wood-paneled ceiling, wood siding and concrete floor. A single overhead light is lit. The man drives the vehicle forward and then makes a sharp right turn out of frame.  There are no sound effects or music in the video.  The clip lasts about 20 seconds.

The video shows a security camera footage of a house's driveway. A palm tree is in the foreground. There is a white car, a black car, and a light gray car parked in the driveway. A person in a dark tank top and shorts walks toward the white car. The date is 08/07/2024 and the time is 07:00:44. The sound of a car engine starting is heard toward the end of the video.

The video is from a security camera in a kitchen. The view is from the countertop, looking into the kitchen and dining area.  The kitchen is on the left and the dining area is on the right. The dining area has a small table with two white chairs. A couch is next to the table. The camera is pointed toward the couch and dining table. The couch has a throw blanket and pillows. There is a window on the back wall, with white curtains. There are three framed pictures on the wall behind the couch. The floor is patterned with light and dark brown tiles. There is a cup and saucer on the counter in the foreground, and a roll of paper towels is in the lower left corner of the frame. The date and time are in the upper left corner of the screen. A logo for the security camera company is in the bottom left corner of the screen. The video shows the room for about 30 seconds and does not capture any action.  There is no sound.  The video appears to have been recorded in the early morning hours.

The video is a short, silent clip of a grassy hill with trees in the background. It appears to be a backyard of a house. A small concrete path is visible in the foreground. The wind is blowing, causing the trees to sway and a thin, horizontal line on the roof to move. There's a logo for the camera brand "YI" in the bottom left corner.  The overall tone of the video is calm and peaceful.

The video begins with a grainy black and white image of a person walking towards the camera in a dimly lit space.  As the video progresses, the lighting and picture quality improves and we see that the person is walking into a gym.  The gym appears to be empty at the time.  The camera shows various gym equipment in the space, including a wall of weight plates, a pull-up bar, and a rack of dumbbells.   The gym is clean and well-maintained.  There are no other people in the video.  A timestamp appears in the top left corner of the screen, but it is difficult to read in the dark lighting of the space.

The video shows a security camera view of a small store or shop. The camera is placed in the bottom left corner of the room, looking towards a doorway on the right side of the frame and some shelves in the background. The floor is covered in white tiled squares, and in the left corner are a few boxes of candy on a shelf. The doorway is open, and the room beyond is illuminated in a pink color.  There is some movement from a pair of feet in the doorway for a brief period, but they do not come completely into frame.

The video is a black and white recording from a security camera. It shows the exterior of a house, with a window, a door, and a small porch. The porch is empty, and there is a motion sensor light hanging from the wall. The video is timestamped 08/07/2024 02:00:18. The camera is pointed at the porch, and there is no movement for the duration of the video.  A single beep is heard at the end of the video.

The video shows a close-up view of a tree with lush green leaves and a few brown leaves. The tree is swaying gently in the breeze. There are a few small, red flowers in the tree, barely visible.  The leaves obscure the view of the background, but a white building is visible in the distance through the leaves. The date and time are displayed in the top left corner of the screen. The sound of the wind is heard, and birds chirping in the background. The video is shot on a still camera and the leaves are moving from left to right, gently swaying in the breeze.

The video is in black and white and shows a room with a TV mounted on the wall. There is a bookshelf to the right of the TV filled with toys.  The camera is positioned in the upper right-hand corner of the room looking down at the TV.  The time and date are displayed in the upper left-hand corner.  The video begins with a woman walking from right to left and then leaving the room.  The camera then focuses on the TV for the remainder of the video, during which time a sound of knocking can be heard.

The video is a still shot taken from a security camera. The date and time are displayed in the top left corner. The shot shows a man lying on a white couch, covered by a white sheet. He is wearing a purple t-shirt and black pants. A blue and pink baby crib with toys is visible in the background. Some glasses and a phone are lying on the couch. The video is very still and nothing is moving for the duration of the clip.

The video is a security camera shot from a house’s front yard. It shows a silver SUV parked in the driveway, facing the camera. A young woman, wearing a pink sweater, blue jeans, and glasses, walks past the front of the car. She is looking down and adjusting the sleeves of her sweater. There are clothes drying on a clothesline behind her. The date and time are displayed at the top left of the video. The video is silent.

The video is a night-time security camera recording from a bedroom.  The camera is positioned at the foot of a bed, pointing up towards the headboard.  The room is dark, but the camera's night vision is enabled, showing the outlines of a metal bed frame with a white duvet.  A figure is visible under the duvet, presumably sleeping.
